          "max_width": "650px"
        },
        {
          "_template": "image",
          "size": 1,
          "src": "/the-knife/E275629F-6703-4C4E-AB13-5576D2B9D562_1_105_c.jpeg",
          "alt": "ocean",
          "max_width": "650px"
        },
        {
          "_template": "image",
          "size": 1,
          "src": "/the-knife/168EA9B5-0BF2-4B98-93C7-6A04ED740EF5_1_105_c.jpeg",
          "alt": "ocean",
          "max_width": "650px"
        },
        {
          "_template": "paragraph",
          "text": "During this time, I also cut the handle to length and bored out a hole for the tang. Then I filed in the tang slot on for the bolster, it was my second attempt, the first one was a little too wide in the opening."
        },
